                                 COMPUTE  IND4 = IND4  -  1
           DISPLAY  SETA-01      GO       ROT-PESQ-30.

       ROT-COMB-20.
           IF  IND3      =  IND1 GO       ROT-COMB-00.
           IF  IND4      =   16  COMPUTE  IND2 = IND2  +  1
