           IF  IND1      <      (IND2  +  6)
                                 GO       ROT-COMB-00.
           COMPUTE  IND3     =   IND2  +  6
           COMPUTE  IND2     =   IND2  +  6
           MOVE     11  TO  IND4 GO       ROT-PESQ-20.

